  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Why is my keyboard's laptop locked? How do I fix it?",
  "response": "There could be several reasons why your laptop's keyboard is locked or not working. Here are some common causes and solutions:\n\n1. **Software Issues:**\n   - **Restart your laptop:** Sometimes, simply rebooting your laptop can resolve the issue.\n   - **Update Drivers:** Check if your keyboard driver needs an update. You can do this by going to the Device Manager, finding the keyboard device under the \"Keyboards\" section, right-clicking, and selecting \"Update driver.\"\n   - **Check for Malware:** Run a malware scan to ensure that there is no malicious software affecting your system.\n\n2. **Keyboard Settings:**\n   - **Num Lock or Function Lock:** Ensure that the Num Lock, Function Lock, or other such special keys are not enabled, which could be restricting the keyboard's functionality.\n   - **Filter Keys:** Check if Filter Keys are turned on, which can cause the keyboard to respond differently. You can find this in the \"Ease of Access\" settings on Windows.\n\n3. **Hardware Issues:**\n   - **Reconnect internal Keyboard Cable:** If you are comfortable opening your laptop, you can check if the internal keyboard connector is loose and reconnect it.\n   - **External Keyboard:** Connect an external keyboard to your laptop via USB to see if it's a hardware-specific issue.\n\n4. **BIOS Settings:**\n   - **Enter BIOS/UEFI:** Sometimes, keyboard settings can be modified through BIOS. Restart your laptop and enter the BIOS setup (commonly by pressing the \"F2\", \"Delete\", or \"Esc\" keys during boot). Check if there\u2019s any setting related to the keyboard.\n   \n5. **Accessibility Settings:**\n   - **Windows Sticky Keys:** Make sure Sticky Keys are not enabled unintentionally, as it may change keyboard behavior. You can toggle this off in the Ease of Access settings.\n\nIf none of these solutions work, it might be a more serious hardware issue, and you may need to consult your laptop's manufacturer or a professional technician for further assistance.",
